()=>{ var formData=new FormData(); formData.append('uid',USERID); formData.append('countrycode',COUNTRYCODE); formData.append('partnerid',PARTNER_ID); formData.append('tag','view'); let response= await axios.post(USER_PROFILE,formData,{headers:{'token':localStorage.getItem('token')}}); if(response.status=='200') { var result=response.data; this.setState({response_data:result}) if(result.DOB!='None') { this.setState({startDate:result.DOB}) } setTimeout(()=>this.setState({isLoading:true}),1000) } else { this.setState({isLoading:true}) } } onInputChange=(value,tag)=>{ var orig_data=this.state.response_data; orig_data[tag]=value; this.setState({response_data:orig_data}) } handleChange(value) { this.setState({startDate:value}) } profileUpdate=(e)=>{ e.preventDefault();
